{* help.ecb2fd_module_picker.tpl *}
<p>The module_picker field creates a dropdown of all installed modules to select from.</p>

<pre>{literal}{content_module module=ECB2 field='module' block=test12 label='12: module_picker' default_value=FormBuilder}{/literal}</pre>

<p>Parameters:</p>
<ul>
    <li>field (required) - 'module_picker', alias:'<b>module</b>'</li>
    <li>default_value (optional) - initial value when creating a new page</li>
    <li>description (optional) - adds additional text explanation for editor</li>
</ul>